PSISWORD: Cyber-Knight psi blade

Syntax: psisword

DESCRIPTION:
  Cyber-Knight only. Toggle a blade of psychic energy in your dominant hand.

  Cost: 10 ISP
  Damage: 2d6 MDC (penetrates MDC targets)
  Duration: about five minutes per character level

  Use psisword again to deactivate early.

NOTES:
  Works only while unarmed (no weapon wielded).
  The blade appears as a shimmer in the air on score and in room text.

SEE ALSO: psi, psionics, cyber-knight, combat
